					"numoutlets" : 0,
					"patching_rect" : [ 40.0, 404.0, 860.0, 33.0 ],
					"text" : "v1 designs the speaker→ear plant from the built-in KEMAR HRTF set (computed-plant presets): no measured-plant loading. The design meets the numeric verification gates X1–X6 (crosstalk rejection, robustness, coloration, gain ceiling, determinism) of the AmbiTap perceptual-verification protocol."
				}

			}
